  {
    "ts": "2026-06-25T12:00:00+00:00",
    "headline": "JPMorganChase Names Doug Petno and Troy Rohrbaugh Co-Presidents of the Company",
    "summary": "NEW YORK, June 25, 2026--JPMorgan Chase & Co. (NYSE: JPM) (\"JPMorganChase\" or the \"Firm\") announced today that Doug Petno and Troy Rohrbaugh, Co-CEOs of the Commercial & Investment Bank (\"CIB\"), have been named Co-Presidents of the company, effective immediately. In addition to their new roles, Petno will become sole CEO of the CIB, and Rohrbaugh will become CEO of Consumer and Community Banking (\"CCB\").",
